locality: Ca. 1 km E of bridge over Riv. des Lacs. Bed of small stream (ultrabasic rocks).
Road between Noumea and Yate. Near Lake Yate. Wetland dominated by low herbs and shrubs of Cunonia deplancheri.

Road to Mt. Dzumac, N of Dumbéa, N of pass from Dumbéa to Koealagogumba River valleys. Maquis along roadside. Ultramafic substrate. Collected with J. Munzinger, M. Schlessman, L. Vary, A. Mouly & T. Le Borgne.
